      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The regular meeting of the Spo-\nkane Equal Suffrage club will be\nheld in the chamber of commerce\nassembly room, basement of the\nHutton building, on the evening of\nJanuary instead of January IL.\nBusiness of Importance, election of\nofficers, etc, will come before the\nmeeting. The following interesting\nprogram will be rendered: Inter\nnational Suffrage hymn; piano Sc\nlection, Miss Partridge; nightin-\ngale song, Mrs. Cyril Ward; ad-\ndress, woman Suffrage\" H. L..\nHughes; Evening Love song, Miss\nHazel Coates.\n\n\nA full attendance is desired."
    }
  ]
